  "prompt": "Which is best online shopping site in india for bags?",
  "response": "There are several popular online shopping sites in India where you can find a wide variety of bags. Some of the best options include:\n\n1. **Amazon India** - Offers a vast selection of bags ranging from handbags to backpacks from various brands.\n   \n2. **Flipkart** - A major competitor to Amazon, Flipkart also has a wide range of bags with competitive prices and good discounts.\n\n3. **Myntra** - Known for its fashion-centric offerings, Myntra has a great selection of trendy bags, including designer and branded options.\n\n4. **Snapdeal** - Offers a variety of bags at affordable prices, catering to different styles and preferences.\n\n5. **Ajio** - A fashion-focused platform with a good collection of handbags, totes, and backpacks.\n\n6. **Tata CLiQ** - Provides a mix of contemporary and traditional bags from reputable brands.\n\n7. **Limeroad** - Focuses on women\u2019s fashion, including a diverse range of stylish bags.\n\n8. **Koovs** - Targets a younger audience with trendy and unique bag designs.\n\nWhen choosing an online shopping site, consider factors like product range, prices, discounts, user reviews, and return policies to ensure a satisfactory shopping experience.",
